NS-CWP-005 — DECISION
Purpose: Work assignment and escalation semantics
Scope:
Automated vs manual task assignment
Performance-based reassignment
Escalation to humans or governance
CWP decides how work flows; GGP decides what is allowed.
Mirrors: NS-GGP-005

