Cross-Engine Dependencies
CWP integrates with but does not own:
GGP — governance and authorization
IDN — identity and trust
DAT — execution tasks
PTE — performance and portfolio visibility
SIG — operational signals

Completion Criteria
CWP documentation is complete when:
NS-CWP-000 → NS-CWP-014 exist
Agentic work is observable, auditable, and governable
Humans remain in control of escalation and override